    section(id='hotel-faq')

        h1 Frequently Asked Questions

        h4 What if COVID-19 prevents me from attending?
        p
            | Should COVID-19 affect Bewhiskered 2021, or prevent you from attending the convention, please reach out to the hotel directly. The Marriott will refund your deposit if this occurs.

        h4 I just made a reservation, when will I see the deposit on my bank statement?
        p
            | Please give the hotel three business days to process the deposit. If you’re waiting longer than that please reach out to us at #[a(href='contact@bewhiskeredcon.org') contact@bewhiskeredcon.org].

        h4 Does the hotel have any rollaway beds, cribs, or sleeper sofas?
        p
            | The hotel does not have rollaway beds nor do the rooms have a sleeper sofa in them. Cribs are available upon request but may be subject to availability. Please reach out to the hotel before you arrive should you need a crib.

        h4 What is the earliest time I can check into my room?
        p
            | Check in is at 4 PM, the Marriott will do its best to accommodate attendees should they arrive earlier.

        h4 How old do I have to be to check into my room?
        p
            | The hotel requires that you are at least 21 years old to check into your hotel.
